<title>UK: London Bridge in talks on significant buy.</title>
<headline>London Bridge in talks on significant buy.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-06-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>London Bridge Software Holdings Plc said on Monday that it is in the process of negotiating &quot;a significant acquisition&quot;.</p>
<p>It said in a statement that the purchase is likely to be funded through a rights issue.</p>
<p>The company expects to make a further announcement on July 4, 1997.</p>
<p>--London Newsroom +44 171 542 4019</p>
